OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5F'Monster' cut wife's body  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Finto over 200 pieces       
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An "evil monster" stabbed his wife to  
OL,6, death then cut her body into more than 
OL,7, 200 pieces before dumping her remains  
OL,8, in a river days later, a court heard.  
OL,10,FHolly Bramley's body parts were found  
OL,11,Fin the River Witham in March 2023.     
OL,13,FNicholas Metson, 28, of Shuttleworth   
OL,14,FHouse, Lincoln, admitted her murder and
OL,15,Fis due to be sentenced on Monday.      
OL,17,FLincoln Crown Court heard he paid his  
OL,18,Ffriend, Joshua Hancock, to dispose of  
OL,19,Fhis wife's remains after being kept    
OL,20,Fhidden in their flat for nearly a week.
